  - POST /auth/forgot-password
    - Input: { email }
    - Output: { message } or error code
  - POST /auth/reset-password
    - Input: { token, newPassword }
    - Output: { message } or error code
- Security:
  - Passwords must be stored securely (hashing with bcrypt/scrypt/Argon2)
  - Tokens should be time-bound and single-use; avoid including sensitive data in the token
